a4f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.brown.edu/Departments/Joukowsky_Institute/courses/urbanism/files/2990585.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brown.edu%2FDepartments%2FJoukowsky_Institute%2Fcourses%2Furbanism%2Ffiles%2F2990585.jpg&h=e0a12bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://treasuresegypt.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/akhenaten-nefertiti-1024x768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftreasuresegypt.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fakhenaten-nefertiti-1024x768.jpg&h=9bb2d5e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/877/40591170704_8d596c892f_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F877%2F40591170704_8d596c892f_c.jpg&h=a2cbece6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/c2/d9/04/c2d9049cf42b38da25edc220b16e8c79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fc2%2Fd9%2F04%2Fc2d9049cf42b38da25edc220b16e8c79.jpg&h=0d126ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然我唔信有外星人嚟過地球，但係呢個法老嘅形象真係cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係嚇死小朋友<br />\n<br />\nbtw呢個佢老婆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/58/18/8b/58188b36ae088c95f8b269e2076aecee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F58%2F18%2F8b%2F58188b36ae088c95f8b269e2076aecee.jpg&h=46d4711f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家都係唔知佢係邊個嘅話，呢個係佢嘅仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://wallpapercave.com/wp/wp3223647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwallpapercave.com%2Fwp%2Fwp3223647.jpg&h=659be9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖坦卡門"},{"pid":"f9eafd6d168f451c34083352e4a559478f0bf60a","tid":1107232,"uid":192078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35070c9079275e206797a16784d58d38c2c1ccd6","tid":1107232,"uid":90